{"tid":183230,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬Facebook粉絲數率先達到1億大關","createTime":"2017-04-02T02:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T03:20:37.000Z","uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03866c9f7c3bd38910d32cd1d9c78c5f4c356e44","tid":183230,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T02:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.sportscn.com/q.jpg?https://c1.hoopchina.com.cn/uploads/star/event/images/170402/eb9bd8370b5328bb748e4a41e803a9e612bbcbda.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.sportscn.com%2Fq.jpg%3Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fc1.hoopchina.com.cn%2Fuploads%2Fstar%2Fevent%2Fimages%2F170402%2Feb9bd8370b5328bb748e4a41e803a9e612bbcbda.png&h=739cd7ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本月底，決定本賽季西甲冠軍爭奪的西班牙國家德比即將在伯納烏球場打響，然而在這之前，皇馬和巴薩已經在Facebook上打響了前哨戰。<br />\n<br />\n此前，兩支球隊的Facebook粉絲數都已經超過了9950萬，他們都有望突破Facebook主頁粉絲1億人次大關，成為首個達成這一里程碑的俱樂部。此前，巴薩的粉絲數還領先於皇馬，然而近幾天這一情況發生了逆轉，皇馬Facebook的粉絲數迅速攀升，並且在今天凌晨正式突破了1億大關。為此，皇馬官方還特意製作了一張圖片（題圖）慶祝這一里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n巴薩昨天為了能夠衝擊1億大關，不惜在社交網站發私信拉票，不少球迷都收到了來自巴薩官方賬號的私信，希望能夠關注巴薩的Facebook主頁幫助他們突破1億粉絲大關。但是最終皇馬還是搶先一步，達到了這個體育界尚無先例的里程碑數字。"},{"pid":"b2dbbb95cae987a1430bf85282087a6bc61cd1b4","tid":183230,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T02:49:49.000Z","msg":"Ig巴塞贏緊"},{"pid":"2d37ca66633e1ee8e0ab554b0033e324b44ae0c7","tid":183230,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T02:55:41.000Z","msg":"有咩好鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5660dd6daf1cb10a7d9a15a9c40abfb72c2b4fb","tid":183230,"uid":7099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:20:37.000Z","msg":"100m=100萬下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恥笑開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}